## Available Skills

Skills extend capabilities with specialized knowledge and workflows.
Location: `~/.local/share/ai-skills/{skill-name}/`

Each skill contains:
- `SKILL.md` - Main instructions (read first)
- `scripts/` - Executable utilities (optional)
- `references/` - Detailed docs (optional)
- `assets/` - Templates/resources (optional)

**Document Skills**: pdf, docx, xlsx, pptx
**Builder Skills**: mcp-builder, skill-creator, artifacts-builder, web-artifacts-builder
**Design Skills**: canvas-design, theme-factory, algorithmic-art, generative-art-algorithms
**Development Skills**: api-design-patterns, testing-patterns, deployment-cicd, nextjs-fullstack-patterns
**Planning Skills**: speckit
**Enterprise Skills**: internal-comms, webapp-testing, brand-guidelines
**Professional Skills**: cv-resume-builder, interview-preparation, portfolio-presentation, networking-outreach
